		Retirees


Main Content​Currently over one hundred two thousand people draw a monthly benefit from Kentucky Retirement Systems, either as a retiree or as a beneficiary of a deceased retiree.  Retirement brings many changes to the lives of our members, and when or how to retire is one of the biggest decisions we all face.  Learn more about the retirement process, the benefits provided to our retirees, and what retirees can do to re-enter the workforce.




