Page Content
Home > 
   RetirementKentucky Retirement SystemsYour future security and ability to reach your retirement goals are important to us.  The Kentucky Retirement System (KRS) is a defined benefit plan, providing a guaranteed payout at retirement.  There are also disability and death benefits available to KRS members and their beneficiaries. For more information about Kentucky Retirement Systems, please visit their 
   website. 















